[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":451},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F":428,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F":437},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F27\u002Flearn-hexo-14-hueman-theme\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":410,"date":411,"description":18,"extension":412,"lang":413,"meta":414,"navigation":415,"path":416,"readingMinutes":417,"seo":418,"standalone":419,"stem":420,"tags":421,"tldr":425,"updated":425,"url":426,"__hash__":427},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F14-試著學-Hexo-主題篇-Hueman-主題.md","(14) 試著學 Hexo - 主題篇 - Hueman 主題","1530073462",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":404},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,31,38,45,48,54,57,65,81,98,104,107,114,128,145,167,176,188,193,196,202,209,218,222,228,231,275,288,354,360,366,381,387,394,397,400],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來我們要來嘗試安裝我們的第一個主題，當然後面還會有一些主題安裝，最主要是熟悉安裝主題的流程。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"安裝-hueman","安裝 Hueman",[16,24,25,26,30],{},"Hexo 在安裝任何主題時都會使用到 git 的指令，其中一個就是 ",[27,28,29],"code",{},"git clone","，因此至少你必須看過甚至知道這個指令的存在，否則你會滿滿的 WT..？",[16,32,33,34,37],{},"首先我們要先開啟終端機，並將路徑 ",[27,35,36],{},"cd"," 到我們的 Hexo 專案(如果你很懶的話，就用 VSCode 也可以)",[16,39,40],{},[41,42],"img",{"alt":43,"src":44},"終端機","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-12%2022.02.12.png",[16,46,47],{},"接下來點一下主題的 GitHub Code 按鈕，並按一下箭頭所指的地方複製連結",[16,49,50],{},[41,51],{"alt":52,"src":53},"複製專案連結","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-12%2022.04.45.png",[16,55,56],{},"然後在終端機的地方輸入以下指令",[16,58,59,60,64],{},"( ",[61,62,63],"del",{},"我知道你可能會很懶惰，所以我直接貼給你。"," )",[66,67,72],"pre",{"className":68,"code":69,"language":70,"meta":71,"style":71},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fppoffice\u002Fhexo-theme-hueman.git themes\u002Fhueman\n","cmd","",[27,73,74],{"__ignoreMap":71},[75,76,79],"span",{"class":77,"line":78},"line",1,[75,80,69],{},[16,82,83,84,86,87,93,94,97],{},"前面的 ",[27,85,29],{}," 我就不解釋了，接下來的 ",[88,89,90],"a",{"href":90,"rel":91},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fppoffice\u002Fhexo-theme-hueman.git",[92],"nofollow"," 則是我們剛剛複製的路徑，而最後的「",[27,95,96],{},"themes\u002Fhueman","」意思是說，我要將專案下載到 themes 的 hueman 資料夾內，因此當你輸入完畢後就可以看到 theme 多了一個 hueman 資料夾，而這個資料夾底下就是我們的主題模板",[16,99,100],{},[41,101],{"alt":102,"src":103},"hueman","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-12%2022.10.59.png",[12,105,106],{"id":106},"切換主題",[16,108,109,110,113],{},"接下來我們必須去 Hexo 的 ",[27,111,112],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml"," 設置剛剛 clone 下來的主題。",[16,115,116,117,120,121,123,124,127],{},"這邊還是要提醒一下，通常 Hexo 本身會有一個系統 ",[27,118,119],{},"_config.yml"," 設置檔，而 Themes 通常也會有一個一樣的檔案，只要只要我是修改 Hexo 的設置檔，那麼我就會打 ",[27,122,112],{}," 而主題則是 ",[27,125,126],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml","。",[16,129,130,131,133,134,137,138,141,142,127],{},"回歸正題，我們打開 ",[27,132,112],{},"，並搜尋 ",[27,135,136],{},"Extensions"," 或是 ",[27,139,140],{},"theme","，然後後面打上主題資料夾的名稱，舉例來講目前我們要使用的主題資料夾名稱是 hueman，那麼就要修改成 ",[27,143,144],{},"theme: hueman",[16,146,147,148,151,152,155,156,158,159,162,163,166],{},"這時候若你輸入 ",[27,149,150],{},"hexo s"," 並前往 ",[27,153,154],{},"http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:4000\u002F","，你會發現出現一些錯誤，這是因為 hueman 主題在 ",[27,157,29],{}," 下來之後，並沒有 ",[27,160,161],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml","，而是只有一個 ",[27,164,165],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml.example","，這時候你只需要輸入以指令即可",[66,168,170],{"className":68,"code":169,"language":70,"meta":71,"style":71},"cp themes\u002Fhueman\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fhueman\u002F_config.yml\n",[27,171,172],{"__ignoreMap":71},[75,173,174],{"class":77,"line":78},[75,175,169],{},[16,177,178,179,181,182,184,185,187],{},"這一段指令的意思就是，我要複製一份 ",[27,180,165],{}," 並且名稱叫做 ",[27,183,161],{},"，接下來你在輸入 ",[27,186,150],{},"，就可以正常顯示囉",[16,189,190],{},[41,191],{"alt":102,"src":192},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1597244970553.jpg",[16,194,195],{},"最後如果你發現你主題切換過去卻是不正常顯示的，例如像是下方一樣",[16,197,198],{},[41,199],{"alt":200,"src":201},"不正常顯示","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-12%2023.10.54.png",[16,203,204,205,208],{},"這時候你可以嘗試看一下 ",[27,206,207],{},"http:\u002F\u002F127.0.0.1:4000\u002F"," 是否正常顯示，若正常顯示的話，你只需要清除瀏覽器的 cookies 就可以解決囉。",[16,210,211,212,217],{},"而這邊 Hueman 的使用代表人物就是...我們的卡斯伯大大(幫他置入性行銷)，如果有興趣的人可以看看，",[88,213,216],{"href":214,"rel":215},"https:\u002F\u002Fwcc723.github.io\u002F",[92],"連結","在此。",[12,219,221],{"id":220},"hueman-的設置","Hueman 的設置",[16,223,224,225,227],{},"接下來讓我們打開 ",[27,226,161],{}," 了解一下該主題有哪些設置可以使用。",[16,229,230],{},"以 Hueman 來講主要的功能設置有以下八大類",[232,233,234,240,245,250,255,260,265,270],"ul",{},[235,236,237],"li",{},[27,238,239],{},"Menus",[235,241,242],{},[27,243,244],{},"Customize",[235,246,247],{},[27,248,249],{},"Widgets",[235,251,252],{},[27,253,254],{},"Search",[235,256,257],{},[27,258,259],{},"Comment",[235,261,262],{},[27,263,264],{},"Share",[235,266,267],{},[27,268,269],{},"Plugins",[235,271,272],{},[27,273,274],{},"Miscellaneous",[16,276,277,278,280,281,283,284,287],{},"通常比較會改到的地方大概就是 ",[27,279,239],{},"，例如我們想要新增一個頁面是專門放作品的，那麼就可以在 ",[27,282,239],{}," 底下新增(請記得使用 ",[27,285,286],{},"hexo pages working"," 指令新增頁面)，通常分號前面會是我們顯示的選單名稱，例如你叫 Working 那麼就會顯示 Working",[66,289,293],{"className":290,"code":291,"language":292,"meta":71,"style":71},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","menu:\n    Home: \u002F\n    # Delete this row if you don't want categories in your header nav bar\n    Categories:\n    About: \u002Fabout\u002Findex.html\n    Working: \u002F\n","yml",[27,294,295,305,318,325,333,344],{"__ignoreMap":71},[75,296,297,301],{"class":77,"line":78},[75,298,300],{"class":299},"sKpQp","menu",[75,302,304],{"class":303},"sMAXC",":\n",[75,306,308,311,314],{"class":77,"line":307},2,[75,309,310],{"class":299},"    Home",[75,312,313],{"class":303},": ",[75,315,317],{"class":316},"sTRMh","\u002F\n",[75,319,321],{"class":77,"line":320},3,[75,322,324],{"class":323},"sQrFR","    # Delete this row if you don't want categories in your header nav bar\n",[75,326,328,331],{"class":77,"line":327},4,[75,329,330],{"class":299},"    Categories",[75,332,304],{"class":303},[75,334,336,339,341],{"class":77,"line":335},5,[75,337,338],{"class":299},"    About",[75,340,313],{"class":303},[75,342,343],{"class":316},"\u002Fabout\u002Findex.html\n",[75,345,347,350,352],{"class":77,"line":346},6,[75,348,349],{"class":299},"    Working",[75,351,313],{"class":303},[75,353,317],{"class":316},[16,355,356,357],{},"接下來畫面上就會直接呈現，但是會有一個雷點，也就是實際出現的是 ",[27,358,359],{},"index.working",[16,361,362],{},[41,363],{"alt":364,"src":365},"index.Working","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2015.12.51.png",[16,367,368,369,372,373,376,377,380],{},"而這邊最主要原因是 Hueman 在選單上是採用語系包去呈現的，因此你必須去調整並增加相對應的名稱到語系包中，例如我們目前所使用的語系是 en，那麼就要開啟 ",[27,370,371],{},"theme\u002Flanguages\u002Fen.yml"," 並增加一行叫做 ",[27,374,375],{},"working: 'Working'","，分好前面是對應 menu 的 ",[27,378,379],{},"Working"," 名稱，而分號後方字串則是預計要顯示的字",[16,382,383],{},[41,384],{"alt":385,"src":386},"working","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2015.21.15.png",[16,388,389,390,393],{},"如果你是設置中文語系的話，那麼作法也是一樣，只是改找 ",[27,391,392],{},"theme\u002Flanguages\u002Fzh-TW.yml"," 而已。",[16,395,396],{},"由於 Hueman 的功能比較簡潔，但可以滿足大部分需求，因此就不再次詳細介紹，在這邊可以自己抓下來玩玩看唷~",[16,398,399],{},"那麼接下來我們下一個主題見~",[401,402,403],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}",{"title":71,"searchDepth":307,"depth":307,"links":405},[406,407,408,409],{"id":14,"depth":307,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":307,"text":22},{"id":106,"depth":307,"text":106},{"id":220,"depth":307,"text":221},"Hexo","2020-09-27 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F14-hexo-hueman","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F14-試著學-Hexo-主題篇-Hueman-主題",[410,422,423,424],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽","Hueman",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200927\u002F1530073462\u002F","vT-R5as19FZL2HwlgLLJzVVz5_-KgSo2Y_fOZpGr2dw",{"newer":429,"older":433},{"url":430,"title":431,"date":432},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F","(15) 試著學 Hexo - 主題篇 - Vexo 主題","2020-09-28 00:00:01",{"url":434,"title":435,"date":436},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200926\u002F2385003709\u002F","(13) 試著學 Hexo - 主題篇 - Hexo 主題如何挑選","2020-09-26 08:26:35",[438,443,447],{"url":439,"title":440,"date":441,"readingMinutes":442},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35","2",{"url":444,"title":445,"date":446,"readingMinutes":417},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","2020-11-01 13:21:00",{"url":448,"title":449,"date":450,"readingMinutes":442},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F","(32)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",1784012795030]